snippet.title: Prem E Pagol | Haripada Bandwala | Ankush | Nusrat | Indraadip Dasgupta | Pathikrit | 2016

localized.description:
Celebrate the madness of love with 'Prem E Pagol' the jazziest song of the season from the film 'Haripada Bandwala'. The song is composed by Indraadip Das Gupta and sung by Arijit Dev, Biswajeeta Deb & Swarnali Bhowmick.
